nth's election defeat\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her swim, which appeared designed to pre-empt Ms Hidalgo's dip, did not go entirely according to plan - she slipped on the riverbank and then slid into the water.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2636, \"end\": 2643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999999997205578, \"rank\": 2.7936057507122814e-10, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her swim\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"plan\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverbank\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Macron had also vowed to swim the Seine earlier this year but did not join.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2753, \"end\": 2759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.91868688206406e-18, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 2787, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999997710347, \"rank\": 1.1724388835112377e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Ms Hidalgo - whose left-wing Socialist party is on the rise in the wake of elections - led a highly choreographed event.\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2961, \"